sentences: Celeste Carballo (born September 21, 1956, Buenos Aires, Argentina) is an Argentine singer-songwriter rock, blues, hard rock, punk and tango.
In the late 1980s, she made public her homosexuality and publicly confessed her romance with fellow singer Sandra Mihanovich.
She became known in the early 1980s for her distinctive voice range from B2 to F#6 in head voice.
